{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01BiXsdRZ5VsvsHTy6s5J3wQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01AAMUUXHmsTuByrqnFLZytc","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Refactor DAO impl files","prompt":"I need you to refactor all DAO implementation files in the Jakarta EE Pet Clinic project to work with Quarkus. The working directory is /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output\n\nFor each DAO implementation file, make these changes:\n1. Replace `import jakarta.ejb.Stateless;` with `import jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;` and `import jakarta.transaction.Transactional;`\n2. Replace `@Stateless` annotation with `@ApplicationScoped` and `@Transactional`\n3. Replace `@EJB` with `@Inject` (add `import jakarta.inject.Inject;`)\n4. Remove `import jakarta.ejb.PostActivate;`, `import jakarta.ejb.PrePassivate;` and their associated methods\n5. Change `@PersistenceContext(unitName = PERSISTENCE_UNIT_NAME)` to just `@PersistenceContext`\n6. Keep `@PostConstruct`, `@PreDestroy`, and all JPA operations as-is\n\nHere are the files to refactor:\n1. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerDaoImpl.java\n2. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetDaoImpl.java\n3. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeDaoImpl.java\n4. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/db/SpecialtyDaoImpl.java\n5. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/db/VetDaoImpl.java\n6. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitDaoImpl.java\n\nRead each file first, then write the refactored version. Make sure to preserve all business logic.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":842,"cache_read_input_tokens":128074,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_