{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01BiXsdRZ5VsvsHTy6s5J3wQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01FTRXNK5vSc4hR7aJyG8GTY","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Refactor Endpoint and Util files","prompt":"I need you to refactor all REST Endpoint files AND EndpointUtil files in the Jakarta EE Pet Clinic project to work with Quarkus. The working directory is /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output\n\nFor ENDPOINT files, make these changes:\n1. Replace `import jakarta.ejb.Stateless;` with `import jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;`\n2. Replace `import jakarta.ejb.EJB;` with `import jakarta.inject.Inject;`\n3. Replace `@Stateless` annotation with `@ApplicationScoped`\n4. Replace all `@EJB` annotations with `@Inject`\n5. Remove `implements Serializable` and `serialVersionUID` (not needed for REST endpoints in Quarkus)\n6. Keep all `@GET`, `@Path`, `@Produces`, `@PathParam` - these work as-is in Quarkus\n7. Remove `import jakarta.xml.bind.JAXBException;` and remove `throws JAXBException` from method signatures (Quarkus handles this automatically)\n\nFor ENDPOINT UTIL files, make the same changes:\n1. Replace `@Stateless` with `@ApplicationScoped`\n2. Replace `@EJB` with `@Inject`\n3. Remove JSON-B related code (JsonbBuilder, Jsonb, etc.) since we use Jackson\n4. Remove JAXB marshalling methods (JAXBContext, Marshaller, etc.) since Quarkus handles serialization\n5. Keep the dtoFactory() and dtoListFactory() methods - those are still needed\n6. Clean up unused imports\n\nHere are the endpoint files:\n1. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/OwnerEndpoint.java\n2. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/PetEndpoint.java\n3. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetTypeEndpoint.java\n4. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/SpecialtyEndpoint.java\n5. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/VetEndpoint.java\n6. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/VisitEndpoint.java\n\nHere are the EndpointUtil files:\n7. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerEndpointUtil.java\n8. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/api/PetEndpointUtil.java\n9. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/api/PetTypeEndpointUtil.java\n10. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/api/SpecialtyEndpointUtil.java\n11. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/api/VetEndpointUtil.java\n12. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/api/VisitEndpointUtil.java\n\nRead each file first, then write the refactored version. Make sure to preserve all REST endpoint paths and all DTO factory logic.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":842,"cache_read_input_tokens":128074,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":842,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":3274},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"faf55576-b919-4f0c-9954-ff7c05fa2fb1","uuid":"c948b211-fd43-40c6-a045-df39029bc1b4"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01BiXsdRZ5VsvsHTy6s5J3wQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01JEMaBjBP5mgGG9ua8vwwde","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Refactor DTO and config files","prompt":"I need you to refactor all DTO files and configuration files in the Jakarta EE Pet Clinic project to work with Quarkus (using Jackson instead of JSON-B). The working directory is /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output\n\nFor ALL DTO files, make these changes:\n1. Replace `import jakarta.json.bind.annotation.JsonbProperty;` with `import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty;`\n2. Replace `import jakarta.json.bind.annotation.JsonbDateFormat;` with `import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonFormat;`\n3. Replace `@JsonbProperty` with `@JsonProperty`\n4. Replace `@JsonbDateFormat(value = \"yyyy-MM-dd\")` with `@JsonFormat(shape = JsonFormat.Shape.STRING, pattern = \"yyyy-MM-dd\")`\n5. Keep `@XmlRootElement` and JAXB annotations - Quarkus supports JAXB for XML output\n6. Keep all Lombok annotations, validation annotations, and Serializable\n\nHere are the DTO files:\n1. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerDto.java\n2. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerListDto.java\n3. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/api/PetDto.java\n4. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/api/PetListDto.java\n5. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/api/PetTypeDto.java\n6. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/api/PetTypeListDto.java\n7. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/api/SpecialtyDto.java\n8. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/api/SpecialtyListDto.java\n9. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/api/VetDto.java\n10. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/api/VetListDto.java\n11. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/api/VisitDto.java\n12. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/api/VisitListDto.java\n\nAlso refactor the Application configuration class:\n13. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/conf/PetclinicApplication.java\n    - This should become a simple JAX-RS Application class with @ApplicationPath(\"/rest\")\n    - Remove references to MessageProvider and FacesContext\n    - Remove @Named annotation\n    - Keep @ApplicationScoped and @ApplicationPath\n\nRead each file first, then write the refactored version.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":842,"cache_read_input_tokens":128074,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":842,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":3274},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"faf55576-b919-4f0c-9954-ff7c05fa2fb1","uuid":"c3506772-5bb4-44c7-9275-80ad314dc74d"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I need you to refactor all DAO implementation files in the Jakarta EE Pet Clinic project to work with Quarkus. The working directory is /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output\n\nFor each DAO implementation file, make these changes:\n1. Replace `import jakarta.ejb.Stateless;` with `import jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;` and `import jakarta.transaction.Transactional;`\n2. Replace `@Stateless` annotation with `@ApplicationScoped` and `@Transactional`\n3. Replace `@EJB` with `@Inject` (add `import jakarta.inject.Inject;`)\n4. Remove `import jakarta.ejb.PostActivate;`, `import jakarta.ejb.PrePassivate;` and their associated methods\n5. Change `@PersistenceContext(unitName = PERSISTENCE_UNIT_NAME)` to just `@PersistenceContext`\n6. Keep `@PostConstruct`, `@PreDestroy`, and all JPA operations as-is\n\nHere are the files to refactor:\n1. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerDaoImpl.java\n2. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetDaoImpl.java\n3. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeDaoImpl.java\n4. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/db/SpecialtyDaoImpl.java\n5. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/db/VetDaoImpl.java\n6. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitDaoImpl.java\n\nRead each file first, then write the refactored version. Make sure to preserve all business logic."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01AAMUUXHmsTuByrqnFLZytc","session_id":"faf55576-b919-4f0c-9954-ff7c05fa2fb1","uuid":"af3d0500-1d45-4469-a50f-65aa1f207a30"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I need you to refactor all Service implementation files in the Jakarta EE Pet Clinic project to work with Quarkus. The working directory is /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output\n\nFor each Service implementation file, make these changes:\n1. Replace `import jakarta.ejb.Stateless;` with `import jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;` and `import jakarta.transaction.Transactional;`\n2. Replace `import jakarta.ejb.EJB;` with `import jakarta.inject.Inject;`\n3. Replace `@Stateless` annotation with `@ApplicationScoped` and `@Transactional`\n4. Replace all `@EJB` annotations with `@Inject`\n5. Keep `@PostConstruct`, `@PreDestroy`, and all business logic as-is\n\nHere are the files to refactor:\n1. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/db/OwnerServiceImpl.java\n2. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/db/PetServiceImpl.java\n3. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/db/PetTypeServiceImpl.java\n4. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/db/SpecialtyServiceImpl.java\n5. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/db/VetServiceImpl.java\n6. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/db/VisitServiceImpl.java\n\nRead each file first, then write the refactored version. Make sure to preserve all business logic."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01GCbivmYGVA3gtPmE7Q2txe","session_id":"faf55576-b919-4f0c-9954-ff7c05fa2fb1","uuid":"07b3ce13-c80f-4ba8-9291-d92f40435f1e"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I need you to refactor all REST Endpoint files AND EndpointUtil files in the Jakarta EE Pet Clinic project to work with Quarkus. The working directory is /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output\n\nFor ENDPOINT files, make these changes:\n1. Replace `import jakarta.ejb.Stateless;` with `import jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;`\n2. Replace `import jakarta.ejb.EJB;` with `import jakarta.inject.Inject;`\n3. Replace `@Stateless` annotation with `@ApplicationScoped`\n4. Replace all `@EJB` annotations with `@Inject`\n5. Remove `implements Serializable` and `serialVersionUID` (not needed for REST endpoints in Quarkus)\n6. Keep all `@GET`, `@Path`, `@Produces`, `@PathParam` - these work as-is in Quarkus\n7. Remove `import jakarta.xml.bind.JAXBException;` and remove `throws JAXBException` from method signatures (Quarkus handles this automatically)\n\nFor ENDPOINT UTIL files, make the same changes:\n1. Replace `@Stateless` with `@ApplicationScoped`\n2. Replace `@EJB` with `@Inject`\n3. Remove JSON-B related code (JsonbBuilder, Jsonb, etc.) since we use Jackson\n4. Remove JAXB marshalling methods (JAXBContext, Marshaller, etc.) since Quarkus handles serialization\n5. Keep the dtoFactory() and dtoListFactory() methods - those are still needed\n6. Clean up unused imports\n\nHere are the endpoint files:\n1. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/OwnerEndpoint.java\n2. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/PetEndpoint.java\n3. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetTypeEndpoint.java\n4. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/SpecialtyEndpoint.java\n5. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/VetEndpoint.java\n6. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/VisitEndpoint.java\n\nHere are the EndpointUtil files:\n7. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerEndpointUtil.java\n8. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/api/PetEndpointUtil.java\n9. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/api/PetTypeEndpointUtil.java\n10. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/api/SpecialtyEndpointUtil.java\n11. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/api/VetEndpointUtil.java\n12. src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/api/VisitEndpointUtil.java\n\nRead each file first, then write the refactored version. Make sure to preserve all REST endpoint paths and all DTO factory logic."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01FTRXNK5vSc4hR7aJyG8GTY","session_id":"faf55576-b919-4f0c-9954-ff7c05fa2fb1","uuid":"b0a6571d-d030-40c5-83bb-a83439e84db3"}
