`import jakarta.transaction.Transactional;`\n\n**Annotation Replacements:**\n- Replaced `@Stateless` with `@ApplicationScoped` and `@Transactional`\n- Replaced all `@EJB` annotations with `@Inject`\n\n**Preserved Elements:**\n- All `@PostConstruct` and `@PreDestroy` lifecycle methods remain unchanged\n- All business logic remains intact\n- All serialVersionUID constants preserved\n- All method implementations unchanged\n- All other imports and annotations preserved\n\n### Key Differences:\n\n**Jakarta EE (Before):**\n```java\n@Stateless\npublic class OwnerServiceImpl implements OwnerService, Serializable {\n    @EJB\n    private OwnerDao ownerDao;\n}\n```\n\n**Quarkus (After):**\n```java\n@ApplicationScoped\n@Transactional\npublic class OwnerServiceImpl implements OwnerService, Serializable {\n    @Inject\n    private OwnerDao ownerDao;\n}\n```\n\nAll refactoring has been completed successfully with no business logic changes, ensuring the application will work with Quarkus while maintaining the same functionality."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"faf55576-b919-4f0c-9954-ff7c05fa2fb1","uuid":"927fbc82-cb0c-4540-9813-b6243e7cabc6"}
