{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01FTRXNK5vSc4hR7aJyG8GTY","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! All the files have been successfully refactored. Let me provide a comprehensive summary of the changes made.\n\n## Refactoring Summary\n\nI have successfully refactored all 12 REST Endpoint and EndpointUtil files in the Jakarta EE Pet Clinic project to work with Quarkus. Here's a detailed breakdown of the changes:\n\n### Endpoint Files Refactored (6 files):\n\n1. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/OwnerEndpoint.java**\n2. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/PetEndpoint.java**\n3. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/PetTypeEndpoint.java**\n4. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/SpecialtyEndpoint.java**\n5. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/VetEndpoint.java**\n6. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/VisitEndpoint.java**\n\n**Changes Made to Endpoint Files:**\n- Replaced `import jakarta.ejb.Stateless;` with `import jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;`\n- Replaced `import jakarta.ejb.EJB;` with `import jakarta.inject.Inject;`\n- Replaced `@Stateless` annotation with `@ApplicationScoped`\n- Replaced all `@EJB` annotations with `@Inject`\n- Removed `implements Serializable` from class declaration\n- Removed `serialVersionUID` field\n- Removed `import jakarta.xml.bind.JAXBException;`\n- Removed `throws JAXBException` from method signatures (getListAsXml() and getEntityAsXml() methods)\n- Removed unused imports (jakarta.json.bind.* from PetEndpoint)\n- Removed the unused `dtoJsonFactory()` method from PetEndpoint\n- Kept all JAX-RS annotations (@GET, @Path, @Produces, @PathParam) intact\n\n### EndpointUtil Files Refactored (6 files):\n\n7. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerEndpointUtil.java**\n8. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/api/PetEndpointUtil.java**\n9. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/api/PetTypeEndpointUtil.java**\n10. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/api/SpecialtyEndpointUtil.java**\n11. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/api/VetEndpointUtil.java**\n12. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/api/VisitEndpointUtil.java**\n\n**Changes Made to EndpointUtil Files:**\n- Replaced `@Stateless` with `@ApplicationScoped`\n- Replaced `@EJB` with `@Inject` for dependency injection\n- Removed `implements Serializable` from class declaration\n- Removed `serialVersionUID` field\n- Removed all JSON-B related code (JsonbBuilder, Jsonb imports and methods)\n- Removed all JAXB marshalling methods (JAXBContext, Marshaller, etc.)\n- Removed the following methods that are no longer needed in Quarkus:\n  - `dtoJsonFactory()` - removed JSON-B serialization\n  - `dtoListJsonFactory()` - removed JSON-B serialization\n  - `dtoXmlFactory()` - removed JAXB marshalling\n  - `dtoListXmlFactory()` - removed JAXB marshalling\n- Kept the essential `dtoFactory()` and `dtoListFactory()` methods intact\n- Cleaned up unused imports (java.io.StringWriter, jakarta.xml.bind.*, jakarta.json.bind.*)\n\n### Key Benefits of These Changes:\n\n1. **Quarkus Compatibility**: The code now uses CDI (Contexts and Dependency Injection) instead of EJB, which is the standard approach in Quarkus\n2. **Simplified Code**: Removed unnecessary serialization code since Quarkus handles JSON/XML serialization automatically with Jackson and JAXB extensions\n3. **Better Performance**: ApplicationScoped beans are more lightweight than Stateless EJBs in Quarkus\n4. **Preserved Functionality**: All REST endpoint paths and DTO factory logic remain intact\n5. **Clean Architecture**: The refactoring maintains the separation of concerns between endpoints and utility classes\n\nAll REST endpoints are now ready to run in Quarkus with automatic JSON/XML serialization handled by the framework's built-in support for JAX-RS."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"faf55576-b919-4f0c-9954-ff7c05fa2fb1","uuid":"270791d3-8526-433b-ba7a-24c1c6bacefe"}
