{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01JEMaBjBP5mgGG9ua8vwwde","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully refactored all DTO files and the configuration file. Let me provide you with a detailed summary of the changes made:\n\n## Refactoring Complete\n\nI have successfully refactored all 12 DTO files and the PetclinicApplication configuration file to work with Quarkus using Jackson instead of JSON-B.\n\n### DTO Files Refactored (12 files):\n\n**1. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerDto.java**\n   - Replaced `jakarta.json.bind.annotation.JsonbProperty` with `com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty`\n   - Changed all `@JsonbProperty` annotations to `@JsonProperty`\n   - Kept all JAXB annotations (`@XmlRootElement`), Lombok annotations, and validation annotations\n\n**2. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/owner/api/OwnerListDto.java**\n   - Replaced JSON-B imports with Jackson imports\n   - Changed `@JsonbProperty` to `@JsonProperty`\n\n**3. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/api/PetDto.java**\n   - Replaced `jakarta.json.bind.annotation.JsonbDateFormat` with `com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonFormat`\n   - Replaced `jakarta.json.bind.annotation.JsonbProperty` with `com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty`\n   - Changed `@JsonbDateFormat(value = \"yyyy-MM-dd\")` to `@JsonFormat(shape = JsonFormat.Shape.STRING, pattern = \"yyyy-MM-dd\")`\n   - Changed all `@JsonbProperty` annotations to `@JsonProperty`\n\n**4. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pet/api/PetListDto.java**\n   - Replaced JSON-B imports with Jackson imports\n   - Changed `@JsonbProperty(\"pet\")` to `@JsonProperty(\"pet\")`\n\n**5. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/api/PetTypeDto.java**\n   - Replaced JSON-B imports with Jackson imports\n   - Changed all `@JsonbProperty` annotations to `@JsonProperty`\n\n**6. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/pettype/api/PetTypeListDto.java**\n   - Replaced JSON-B imports with Jackson imports\n   - Changed `@JsonbProperty` to `@JsonProperty`\n\n**7. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/api/SpecialtyDto.java**\n   - Replaced JSON-B imports with Jackson imports\n   - Changed all `@JsonbProperty` annotations to `@JsonProperty`\n\n**8. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/specialty/api/SpecialtyListDto.java**\n   - Replaced JSON-B imports with Jackson imports\n   - Changed `@JsonbProperty` to `@JsonProperty`\n\n**9. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/api/VetDto.java**\n   - Replaced JSON-B imports with Jackson imports\n   - Changed all `@JsonbProperty` annotations to `@JsonProperty`\n\n**10. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/vet/api/VetListDto.java**\n   - Replaced JSON-B imports with Jackson imports\n   - Changed `@JsonbProperty` to `@JsonProperty`\n\n**11. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/api/VisitDto.java**\n   - Replaced `jakarta.json.bind.annotation.JsonbDateFormat` with `com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonFormat`\n   - Replaced `jakarta.json.bind.annotation.JsonbProperty` with `com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty`\n   - Changed `@JsonbDateFormat(value = \"yyyy-MM-dd\")` to `@JsonFormat(shape = JsonFormat.Shape.STRING, pattern = \"yyyy-MM-dd\")`\n   - Changed all `@JsonbProperty` annotations to `@JsonProperty`\n\n**12. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/visit/api/VisitListDto.java**\n   - Replaced JSON-B imports with Jackson imports\n   - Changed `@JsonbProperty(\"visit\")` to `@JsonProperty(\"visit\")`\n\n### Configuration File Refactored:\n\n**13. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/woehlke/jakartaee/petclinic/application/conf/PetclinicApplication.java**\n   - Removed `@Named` annotation (not needed for Quarkus JAX-RS application)\n   - Removed all MessageProvider and FacesContext related code\n   - Removed `@PostConstruct` and `@PreDestroy` lifecycle methods\n   - Removed Serializable interface implementation\n   - Simplified to a clean JAX-RS Application class with just `@ApplicationScoped` and `@ApplicationPath(\"/rest\")`\n   - Kept the `@Log` annotation for logging support\n\n### Key Changes Summary:\n\n1. **JSON-B to Jackson Migration**: All DTO files now use Jackson annotations (`@JsonProperty`, `@JsonFormat`) instead of JSON-B annotations (`@JsonbProperty`, `@JsonbDateFormat`)\n\n2. **Date Format**: Changed date formatting from `@JsonbDateFormat(value = \"yyyy-MM-dd\")` to `@JsonFormat(shape = JsonFormat.Shape.STRING, pattern = \"yyyy-MM-dd\")` in PetDto and VisitDto\n\n3. **Preserved Compatibility**: All JAXB annotations (`@XmlRootElement`), Lombok annotations, validation annotations, and Serializable interfaces were preserved to maintain compatibility\n\n4. **Simplified Application Configuration**: The PetclinicApplication class is now a clean, minimal JAX-RS Application class suitable for Quarkus\n\nAll files are now fully compatible with Quarkus using Jackson for JSON serialization/deserialization while maintaining JAXB support for XML output."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"faf55576-b919-4f0c-9954-ff7c05fa2fb1","uuid":"e22e9f20-eeec-4a90-813e-df7142de1702"}
