{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_012aSMjNoQiA2uV2B3W7cRhP","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The migration is complete. Here's the final summary:\n\n---\n\n## Migration Summary: Jakarta EE 10 to Quarkus 3.8.4\n\n**Status**: Complete - All 37 smoke tests passing\n\n### What was done:\n\n1. **Build system**: Replaced the multi-runtime Jakarta EE pom.xml with a Quarkus 3.8.4 build using extensions: resteasy-jackson, resteasy-jaxb, hibernate-orm, jdbc-postgresql, arc, smallrye-health, hibernate-validator, narayana-jta\n\n2. **EJB to CDI**: All `@Stateless` annotations replaced with `@ApplicationScoped` + `@Transactional`; all `@EJB` replaced with `@Inject` across 24 Java files\n\n3. **JSON-B to Jackson**: All DTO annotations migrated from `@JsonbProperty` to `@JsonProperty` and `@JsonbDateFormat` to `@JsonFormat` across 12 DTO classes\n\n4. **JSF removal**: Entire JSF/PrimeFaces view layer removed (not supported in Quarkus) - only the REST API is preserved\n\n5. **Configuration**: `persistence.xml` replaced with `application.properties`; created `import.sql` for database seeding\n\n6. **Dockerfile**: Updated CMD from Liberty runtime to `java -jar target/quarkus-app/quarkus-run.jar`\n\n7. **Testing**: Created `smoke.py` with 37 tests covering all 6 entity endpoints (petType, specialty, vet, owner, pet, visit) in JSON and XML formats, plus health check\n\n### Test results:\n```\n37 passed, 0 failed out of 37 tests\n```"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":131,"cache_read_input_tokens":62622,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":131,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":410},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"faf55576-b919-4f0c-9954-ff7c05fa2fb1","uuid":"6c2209f6-c258-4798-8e7e-3e7275bc3262"}
